ntechnischen Operationen und ihrer repräsentationspolitischen Dimensionen und entfaltet so eine umfassende Zeitdiagnose der digitalen Welt, in der wir leben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aDigitale Medien. 4aMedien. 4aMedientheorie. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aSocial Media. 4aSoziale Netzwerke. 4aWeb 2.0. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aDigital Media.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia Theory.  aMedia.  aSocial Media.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z978311037074408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2013z9783110401219oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839421277zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839421277423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839421277/original  a978-3-11-037074-4  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013c2010d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TGPb2013  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013